snippet.title: Equestria Girls! Motocross Friendship Games
snippet.description:
Discord: https://discord.gg/32JcE3Z

Please use this link to help download Numuki browser, so that you don't have to ask me how to play these flash games in the comment section:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UzZ5kGzbtsQ

Before playing this game, make sure to download "Lightspark" so that you can play the same games in this video and the link will be provided below.
https://lightspark.github.io/
